msgid "Cambiar el slug no afectará tus datos ni filtros guardados. URLs externas, webhooks o integraciones que usen el slug actual deberán actualizarse. Imagina CRM mantendrá redirects automáticos del anterior."
msgstr "Changing the slug will not affect your data or saved filters. External URLs, webhooks, or integrations using the current slug will need to be updated. Imagina CRM will keep automatic redirects from the previous slug."

